WEBVTT

00:12:28.133 --> 00:12:30.596
one će uskoro postati
priče o nama.

00:12:30.900 --> 00:12:32.050
Hvala.

00:12:32.074 --> 00:12:34.772
(Pljesak)

00:12:39.437 --> 00:12:41.437
(Pljesak završava)

00:12:41.849 --> 00:12:43.684
Tom Rielly: Imam nekoliko pitanja.

00:12:43.708 --> 00:12:47.636
U srednjoj školi sam učio o
Povelji o pravima,

00:12:47.660 --> 00:12:50.556
ustavu, slobodi govora,

00:12:50.580 --> 00:12:55.113
pravičnom postupku i oko 25 
drugih zakona i prava

00:12:55.137 --> 00:12:56.921
koji se, izgleda, ovime krše.

00:12:57.706 --> 00:13:00.410
Kako je moguće da se to događa?